    • ContactDetails

      public ContactDetails​(java.lang.String phone, java.lang.String email, java.lang.String town, java.lang.String street, int streetNumber, java.lang.String ZIP, java.lang.String country)
      combines the contact details
      Parameters:
      phone - phone number, it could a mobile number or a home phone number
      email - a simple mail address
      town - were a person live or you can find the place (sight)
      street - a street
      streetNumber - a street number without letters
      ZIP - the zip from the town, its more accurate then town only
      country - it's important, if the journey takes place in several countries
